{"data":[{"date":"09:32 14/07","title":"\"Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p qu\u00ean chung k\u1ebft EURO 2016\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/umtiti-phap-khong-duoc-phep-quen-chung-ket-euro-2016.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti cho r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00ean nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft EURO 2016.</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh khi l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn trong hai n\u0103m qua. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i EURO 2016, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Croatia song trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra t\u1ea1i \u1edf chung k\u1ebft Euro hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p qu\u00ean EURO 2016 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p qu\u00ean EURO 2016 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/5/umtiti-phap-khong-duoc-phep-quen-chung-ket-euro-2016.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Umtiti (22) mu\u1ed1n tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng trong tr\u1eadn\u00a0chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Umtiti n\u00f3i: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 sai \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Euro 2016 \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m. Croatia l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nghi\u00eam t\u00fac nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 Ivan Rakitic v\u00e0 Luka Modric, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam: \"\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng cho Croatia. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf ba tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 Croatia c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. H\u1ecd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed3ng quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti, Paul Pogba c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7: \u201cT\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 nu\u1ed1t tr\u00f4i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c thua m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 n\u00f3 r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf EURO 2016. Khi \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tin ch\u1eafc s\u1ebd th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 d\u1eb7n nhau kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea1m ph\u1ea3i sai l\u1ea7m n\u0103m x\u01b0a\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 22h00 t\u1ed1i mai 15/7 (gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam).</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-hlv-simeone-dua-ra-loi-khuyen-cho-griezmann-421-191147.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-hlv-simeone-dua-ra-loi-khuyen-cho-griezmann.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-hlv-simeone-dua-ra-loi-khuyen-cho-griezmann-421-191147.html\">Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: HLV Simeone \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean cho Griezmann</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai 15/7, HLV Diego Simeone \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Griezmann \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/modric-toi-san-sang-doi-3-cup-c1-de-vo-dich-world-cup-469-191113.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/modric-toi-san-sang-doi-3-cup-c1-de-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/modric-toi-san-sang-doi-3-cup-c1-de-vo-dich-world-cup-469-191113.html\">Modric: T\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i 4 c\u00fap C1 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Modric kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi anh. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u00f2n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u Champions...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ivan-perisic-tiet-lo-ly-do-giup-croatia-co-the-danh-bai-phap-421-191086.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/ivan-perisic-tiet-lo-ly-do-giup-croatia-co-the-danh-bai-phap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ivan-perisic-tiet-lo-ly-do-giup-croatia-co-the-danh-bai-phap-421-191086.html\">Ivan Perisic ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Croatia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p</span><br>\r\nIvan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Les Bleus trong tr\u1eadn chung...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/croatia-truoc-tran-gap-phap-tinh-than-co-khoa-lap-yeu-to-the-luc-421-191115.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/croatia-truoc-tran-gap-phap-tinh-than-co-khoa-lap-yeu-to-the-luc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/croatia-truoc-tran-gap-phap-tinh-than-co-khoa-lap-yeu-to-the-luc-421-191115.html\">Croatia tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p: Tinh th\u1ea7n c\u00f3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c?</span><br>\r\nCroatia \u0111\u00e3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup, tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#333333;mso-fareast-language:=\"\" ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1245","checkdouble":"191148"},{"date":"10:52 14/07","title":"HLV Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Shaqiri c\u1ee7a Liverpool?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-ve-tan-binh-shaqiri-cua-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c sau khi Liverpool ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 t\u1eeb Stoke City v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 13,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-xherdan-shaqiri-172-191137.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xherdan Shaqiri</span> sau khi k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 13,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Stoke City.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield v\u00e0 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 23 quen thu\u1ed9c. Anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 ba gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau hai qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ea3 tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa - Naby Keita t\u1eeb RB Leipzig v\u00e0 Fabinho t\u1eeb Monaco.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Shaqiri t\u00e2n binh Liverpool h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Shaqiri t\u00e2n binh Liverpool h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-ve-tan-binh-shaqiri-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Jurgen Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Shaqiri, t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong h\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">HLV Jurgen Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Shaqiri, t\u00e2n binh h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng trong c\u00f4ng cu\u1ed9c d\u1ef1ng x\u00e2y \u0111\u1ebf ch\u1ebf The Kop: \u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u01b0 Xherdan h\u1ebft.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n \u1edf Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf \u0110\u1ee9c, quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m Premier League v\u00e0 g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ee7 bi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 v\u1eefng \u1edf m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t n\u00e0y. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng lu\u00f4n ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u1eefa.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cXherdan s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n \u2013 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh v\u00e0 li\u1ec1u l\u0129nh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f3 tin tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t cho Liverpool khi linh ho\u1ea1t v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i tin ch\u1eafc v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi, Xherdan s\u1ebd h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 th\u00edch nghi nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u1edbi Liverpool m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Anfield ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u1eadt d\u1eady tr\u1ea7m tr\u1ed3, v\u1ed7 tay t\u00e1n th\u01b0\u1edfng trong m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-xherdan-shaqiri-172-191137.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/chinh-thuc-liverpool-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-xherdan-shaqiri.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-xherdan-shaqiri-172-191137.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri</span><br>\r\nLiverpool ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 Xherdan Shaqiri sau khi k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 13,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Stoke...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1244","checkdouble":"191149"},{"date":"09:23 14/07","title":"Shaqiri h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Salah","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/shaqiri-hao-huc-truoc-co-hoi-da-cap-cung-salah.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Shaqiri t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Mohamed Salah t\u1ea1i Liverpool \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>Shaqiri h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f9ng Salah</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Salah c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Basel sau khi Shaqiri r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. C\u1ea3 hai ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng nhau trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 nh\u01b0ng Shaqiri c\u0169ng c\u00f3 k\u00fd \u1ee9c v\u1ec1 si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-xherdan-shaqiri-172-191137.html\" target=\"_blank\">Shaqiri \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 13.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span> t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u00e0 Stoke. Trong b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft, Shaqiri t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng Salah \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Shaqiri h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Shaqiri h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/shaqiri-hao-huc-truoc-co-hoi-da-cap-cung-salah.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Shaqiri \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Salah t\u1ea1i Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft anh \u1ea5y qu\u00e1 r\u00f5 nh\u01b0ng anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c khi t\u00f4i c\u00f2n \u1edf Basel. Anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n 2 hay 3 l\u1ea7n g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u1eadp v\u1edbi anh \u1ea5y. Sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec t\u00f4i t\u1edbi Bayern c\u00f2n anh \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i Basel.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea5y anh \u1ea5y \u1edf Liverpool. Anh \u1ea5y v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i vui m\u1eebng thay anh \u1ea5y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Salah l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai t\u1ed1t. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec1u mong mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n khi Liverpool kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng n\u0103m nay m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Shaqiri \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn c\u00f9ng Liverpool</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Liverpool t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Champions League trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Bayern. Anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 3 danh hi\u1ec7u V\u0110QG Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 c\u00f9ng Basel. V\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u n\u1eefa \u1edf Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft m\u00f9i v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf Bayern Munich. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0103n ba v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i tin l\u00e0 Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u. C\u00e1c C\u0110V x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f3. Hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-ve-tan-binh-shaqiri-cua-liverpool-172-191149.html\">HLV Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Shaqiri c\u1ee7a Liverpool?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-xherdan-shaqiri-172-191137.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1243","checkdouble":"191150"},{"date":"09:14 14/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 14/7 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/nhan-dinh-hai-phong-vs-binh-duong-17h00-ngay-147-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 14/7 (V\u00f2ng 19 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 147 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 147 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/haiphong-bbd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span>H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: 0-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u1ede giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League 2018, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00edtrong Top 3. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng khi V-League b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c v\u1eeba qua, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Hoa ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ecf to\u00e0n thua 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 8 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng v\u1edbi 23 \u0111i\u1ec3m, h\u01a1n nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi\u1ebfu chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u khi\u1ebfn HLV Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Vi\u1ec7t Ho\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 khi c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t m\u1ecfi m\u1ec7t. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i khi h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i t\u1eeb s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, ph\u00f3 m\u1eb7c cho hai ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ngo\u1ea1i binh l\u00e0 Fagan vs Stevens t\u1ef1 x\u1eed l\u00fd. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng \u00edt ra h\u1ecd v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edfnh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00f2a k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh 4-4 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ea3ng Nam trong \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Ti\u1ebfn Linh l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t hattrick.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 kh\u1eafc tinh c\u1ee7a H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng. Hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng to\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 V-League, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 7 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u1edf L\u1ea1ch Tray (th\u1eafng 4).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN:<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng: V\u0103n L\u00e2m, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Ho\u00e0i D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Ng\u1ecdc T\u00e2n, V\u0103n Ph\u00fa, Qu\u1ed1c Trung, Th\u00e0nh Long, Xu\u00e2n H\u00f9ng, Adriano, Fagan, Stevens.<br>\r\nB\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: T\u1ea5n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, H.T.T\u00e0i, L.T.T\u00e0i, Thanh Th\u1ea3o, Chinedu, Anh T\u00e0i, Ti\u1ebfn Linh, Tanidis, S\u1ef9 Gi\u00e1p, V\u0103n V\u0169, Ho\u00e0ng Max.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1242","checkdouble":"191152"},{"date":"09:17 14/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 14/7: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Colombia t\u1ed1 Barca \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/diem-tin-sang-147-nguoi-hung-colombia-to-barca-doi-xu-te-bac.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Colombia t\u1ed1 Barca \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c, Juve \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Ronaldo, Liverpool s\u1eafp mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 14/7.</h2><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Colombia t\u1ed1 Barca \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yerry Mina \u2013 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o b\u1ecb Barca \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"T\u00f4i nh\u1eadn ra m\u00ecnh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n\u00a0kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean\u00a0trong danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. T\u00f4i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh \u1edf nh\u00e0,\" Mina chia s\u1ebb.\u00a0\"Th\u1eadt\u00a0bu\u1ed3n\u00a0khi ph\u1ea3i\u00a0ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1c\u00a0\u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u qua TV! Ch\u1eb3ng ai mu\u1ed1n\u00a0tr\u1ea3i qua\u00a0c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf\u00a0n\u00e0y\". <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Everton \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Mina v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o\u00a0trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia\u00a0s\u1ebd c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 147 Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Colombia t\u1ed1 Barca \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 147 Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Colombia t\u1ed1 Barca \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Diem-tin-sang-147-Nguoi-hung-Colombia-to-Barca-doi-xu-te-bac-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"width: 779px;\">\r\n            <table style=\"text-align: center; width: 777px;\">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td><em>Mina cho r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u1ea1i Barcelona<br>\r\n                        </em></td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Gianluca Di Mazio c\u1ee7a Sky Sport, Roma \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd h\u1ea1 gi\u00e1 Alisson xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 70 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Liverpool. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao m\u00e0 Roma \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u00e3 bu\u1ed9c L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110\u1ecf ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat lui. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n h\u1ee9ng th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y khi quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Thibaut Courtois c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ra m\u1eaft HLV m\u1edbi<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 sa th\u1ea3i HLV Conte, CLB Chelsea \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ra m\u1eaft HLV ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u1edd Sky Sports Italy \u0111\u01b0a tin HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Brigde. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo c\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n tin, Sarri s\u1ebd k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea trong 2 n\u0103m k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gia h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m. M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng Sarri nh\u1eadn \u1edf Chelsea l\u00e0 5,3 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB, Gianfranco Zola c\u0169ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Sarri tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Juve \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Ronaldo<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Italia, CLB Juventus d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd cho ra m\u1eaft Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 16/7 t\u1edbi sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u euro. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Neymar sang PSG n\u1ebfu t\u00ednh t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Real ch\u01b0a c\u1ea7n mua Neymar<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u201cV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin cho r\u1eb1ng CLV li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Neymar c\u1ee7a PSG, Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m r\u00f5 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. PSG v\u00e0 Real c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 m\u1eadt thi\u1ebft. N\u1ebfu Real quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m l\u00e0 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n\u201d, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>M.U mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Maguire<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo\u00a0Daily Mail,\u00a0CLB Man United \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap Anh h\u1ea1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn B\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup. Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 50 tri\u1ec7u B\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Leicester City nh\u1ea3 Maguire.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>HLV Conte c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc ki\u1ec7n Chelsea v\u00ec \"b\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n\" b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo tin t\u1eeb Sky Sport, HLV\u00a0Antonio Conte\u00a0\u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc\u00a0ki\u1ec7n\u00a0CLB Chelsea\u00a0l\u00ean t\u00f2a \u00e1n c\u1ee7a FIFA n\u1ebfu CLB n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu thanh to\u00e1n ph\u00ed b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a\u00a0The Blues\u00a0v\u1eeba\u00a0c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i\u00a0v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.\u00a0Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2019 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. Tuy nhi\u00ean,\u00a0Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n\u00a0b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng.\u00a0<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam:\u00a0<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-137-mu-co-nguy-co-lon-de-mat-pogba-184-191118.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 13/7: M.U c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Pogba</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Roboto;color:#081F2C\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1241","checkdouble":"191153"},{"date":"09:22 14/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 17h00 ng\u00e0y 14/7 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/nhan-dinh-khanh-hoa-vs-sai-gon-17h00-ngay-147-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 14/7 (V\u00f2ng 19 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 17h00 ng\u00e0y 147 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 17h00 ng\u00e0y 147 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/sai-gon-fc-sanna-khanh-hoa-bvn-vong-21-vleague-2017_1pr850k1l3oyp130epfbjpk5qc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span>Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: 3-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea t\u1eeb qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 cho th\u1ea5y S\u00e0i G\u00f2n lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a khi 5 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng (h\u00f2a 4, thua 1). V\u00ec v\u1eady, d\u00f9 \u0111ang v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u01b0u th\u1ebf s\u00e2n b\u00e3i nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cao b\u1edfi \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u0103ng hoa v\u1edbi 5 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf 7 v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n \u0111ang gi\u1eef v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean BXH.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 18 v\u00f2ng v\u00e0 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 t\u1eeb d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u00ean. N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 l\u1edbn s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u00e0i G\u00f2n d\u0129 nhi\u00ean th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 t\u1ec7 khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua 3/4 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Th\u00eam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, 8 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e3 qua \u1edf V-League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng (thua 5).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf V-League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 thi\u1ebfu ki\u00ean c\u1ed1. T\u00ednh ra, sau 18 tr\u1eadn, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 31 b\u00e0n thua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec v\u1eady, m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n S\u00e0i G\u00f2n chi\u1ec1u nay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- 4 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a.<br>\r\n- C\u1ea3 5 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua m\u1ed1c 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a: Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u2013 Zarour, Tr\u1ecdng B\u00ecnh, \u0110\u00ecnh L\u1ee3i, V\u0103n T\u00f9ng, T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i, Tr\u00f9m T\u1ec9nh, Qu\u1ed1c Ch\u00ed, Trung Hi\u1ebfu, \u0110\u00ecnh Kh\u01b0\u01a1ng, Y.Toure.<br>\r\n+ S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: V\u0103n Phong \u2013 Qu\u1ed1c Long, V\u0103n Ng\u1ecd, \u0110\u1ee9c L\u1ee3i, Ng\u1ecdc Duy, Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, Ho\u00e0ng Thi\u00ean, Xu\u00e2n D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Tr\u1ea7n V\u0169, Anh V\u0169, Da Silva</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1240","checkdouble":"191154"},{"date":"10:01 14/07","title":"Martinez \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/martinez-dat-muc-tieu-danh-bai-dt-anh-o-tran-tranh-hang-ba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Roberto Martinez mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 k\u1ebft th\u00fac World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d.</h2><h2>B\u1ec9 tranh h\u1ea1ng ba c\u00f9ng Anh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Anh b\u1ecb Croatia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua. C\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHai \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng G. B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 1-0. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111o chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c cho s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i khi h\u1ecd d\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n c\u1ed1 thua \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Roberto Martinez cho r\u1eb1ng B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 chung cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Martinez \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Martinez \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/martinez-dat-muc-tieu-danh-bai-dt-anh-o-tran-tranh-hang-ba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Martinez mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T\u00a0Anh \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Khi b\u1ea1n k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 t\u00e2m l\u00fd bu\u00f4ng l\u01a1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Nga \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 th\u00e1ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec1u thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u00e0 c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u00e2m l\u00fd nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. V\u1edbi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i 7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u1ea1c quan khi r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Martinez kh\u00f4ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp gi\u1eefa Kane v\u00e0 Lukaku cho danh hi\u1ec7u Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y V\u00e0ng \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>. Kane \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f2n Lukaku k\u00e9m 2 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng HLV Martinez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Lukaku kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd b\u1ecb t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng trong vi\u1ec7c s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 Lukaku ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Lukaku c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u00fat trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn. B\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 50% c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf t\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng Lukaku th\u00ec quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o hay nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. Pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y Lukaku kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n m\u00e0 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec t\u1eadp th\u1ec3\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-gia-nhap-real-madrid-voi-gia-ky-luc-180-191140.html\">HLV B\u1ec9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Hazard gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-co-nguy-co-mat-3-tru-cot-o-tran-tranh-hang-ba-voi-bi-421-191080.html\">\u0110T Anh c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t 3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng Ba v\u1edbi B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1239","checkdouble":"191155"},{"date":"07:27 14/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh h\u1ea1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/nguoi-anh-ha-quyet-tam-gianh-huy-chuong-dong-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh vs B\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi nhau?</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Croatia \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 khi\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/du-am-anh-vs-croatia-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-421-191004.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anh tan m\u1ed9ng c\u00fap v\u00e0ng</span>, ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 nhau trong tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng mang nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i th\u00ec hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00e0ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c t\u1ed1i nay.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 18 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 18 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/nguoi-anh-ha-quyet-tam-gianh-huy-chuong-dong-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng World Cup 2018. Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 47 tu\u1ed5i:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u00cdt ng\u00e0y qua th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup c\u00f3 20 ph\u00fat, r\u1ed3i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u c\u00f3 10 ph\u00fat hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 tan t\u00e0nh m\u00e2y kh\u00f3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd r\u1ec7u r\u00e3 hay suy s\u1ee5p tinh th\u1ea7n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c cho \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba s\u1eafp t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng World Cup, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng t\u1eebng b\u1ecb B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y. Ai c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n ra s\u00e2n c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean v\u1eb9n nh\u01b0ng l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e0ng \u00edt s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ea3 B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Anh \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eebng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup n\u0103m 1986 v\u00e0 1990. T\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t sau 52 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0, trong khi \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bi-vs-anh-21h00-ngay-147-moi-nguoi-vi-mot-nguoi-421-191141.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/nhan-dinh-bi-vs-anh-21h00-ngay-147-moi-nguoi-vi-mot-nguoi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bi-vs-anh-21h00-ngay-147-moi-nguoi-vi-mot-nguoi-421-191141.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Anh (21h00 ng\u00e0y 14/7): M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00ec m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a nh\u01b0 tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup, c\u1ea3 B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Anh c\u00f3 l\u1ebd v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong th\u1ebf ng\u1ea9ng cao \u0111\u1ea7u,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong> <o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1238","checkdouble":"191139"},{"date":"08:15 14/07","title":"HLV B\u1ec9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Hazard gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-gia-nhap-real-madrid-voi-gia-ky-luc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV Roberto Martinez xoay quanh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Hazard gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Roberto Martinez c\u00f3 v\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ed1ng tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c th\u00ea th\u1ea3m sau khi tan m\u1ed9ng c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady trong t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV B\u1ec9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Real Madrid mua Hazard t\u1eeb Chelsea h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV B\u1ec9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Real Madrid mua Hazard t\u1eeb Chelsea h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-gia-nhap-real-madrid-voi-gia-ky-luc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV B\u1ec9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Real Madrid mua Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ea5p CLB c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mang ra b\u00e0n lu\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Sau khi Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i n\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u1ede Bernabeu, anh s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf ch\u00ednh Cristiano Ronaldo sau khi si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha k\u1ebft th\u00fac 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Juventus.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">HLV Martinez ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Real Madrid mua Hazard, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i: \u201cEden n\u00ean v\u1eady b\u1edfi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea1i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng 1v1, xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 m\u1ecdi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u1ecdi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTr\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Eden ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd t\u1ef1 m\u00e3n hay h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh, kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c, lu\u00f4n n\u00e2ng cao chu\u1ea9n m\u1ef1c v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n v\u00ec t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Real Madrid ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng n\u00ean c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ebf ch\u1ebf xoay quanh Eden.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch cao nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh t\u1ed1i nay (21h00 gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-va-chuyen-tuong-lai-hazard-nga-ba-duong-cho-ca-doi-ben-172-187469.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/chelsea-va-chuyen-tuong-lai-hazard-nga-ba-duong-cho-ca-doi-ben.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-va-chuyen-tuong-lai-hazard-nga-ba-duong-cho-ca-doi-ben-172-187469.html\">Chelsea v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Hazard: Ng\u00e3 ba \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean</span><br>\r\nVi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong> <o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1237","checkdouble":"191140"},{"date":"07:03 14/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (14/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1472018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 14/7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u00f4ng tin ng\u00e0y gi\u1edd c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00eam/r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0