color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>FIFA \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn World Cup 2022 \u1edf Qatar s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng, v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb 21/11 \u0111\u1ebfn 18/12.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Gianni Infantino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp k\u00edn c\u1ee7a FIFA \u1edf Nga: \u201cWorld Cup 2022 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb 21/11 t\u1edbi 18/12 v\u1edbi \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng 48 \u0110TQG tham gia tranh t\u00e0i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u00e0 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Qatar, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh bao nhi\u00eau \u0110TQG s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1, 32 hay nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.\u201d <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, m\u1ecdi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua. V\u1edbi 48 \u0110TQG, nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i khu v\u1ef1c s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft, th\u1ebf n\u00ean t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y.\u201d \u2013 Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng 48 \u0110TQG \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn 2026 m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"World Cup 2022 \u1edf Qatar ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"World Cup 2022 \u1edf Qatar ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/chinh-thuc-world-cup-2022-se-duoc-to-chuc-vao-mua-dong.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>World Cup 2022 \u1edf Qatar ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng, t\u1eeb 21/11 \u0111\u1ebfn 18/12</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Do th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft m\u00f9a h\u00e8 hai th\u00e1ng 6-7 \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c T\u00e2y \u00c1 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t, v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 trung b\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 41,3 \u0111\u1ed9 C k\u00e8m c\u00e1i n\u1eafng ch\u00f3i chang oi \u1ea3, n\u00ean FIFA bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c r\u1eddi World Cup 2022 sang m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n t\u1ea7m 25-29 \u0111\u1ed9 C. C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u0103ng cai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Qatar c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng l\u00e0m m\u00e1t b\u1eb1ng n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ef3 World Cup m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed n\u00e0y \u00e2u c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eafc d\u0129 v\u00ec m\u1ecdi l\u1ee3i \u00edch cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng s\u1ebd g\u00e2y ra x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n l\u1edbn \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. FIFA \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi c\u00f4ng v\u0103n y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1c L\u0110B\u0110 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh h\u1ee3p l\u00fd l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch \u1ee9n, v\u1edbi c\u00e1c CLB s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb 2-3 tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean \u0110TQG.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u0103m 2015, ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch FIFA Jim Boyce l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c World Cup 2022 v\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng: \u201cT\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd sung s\u1ee9c h\u01a1n khi World Cup ch\u1ec9 di\u1ec5n ra trong 28 ng\u00e0y, r\u00fat ng\u1eafn so v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i k\u00e9o d\u00e0i c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1edbm h\u01a1n 3 tu\u1ea7n v\u00e0 k\u1ebft th\u00fac mu\u1ed9n h\u01a1n 3 tu\u1ea7n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-my-mexico-canada-dong-dang-cai-world-cup-2026-421-188418.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/wc.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-my-mexico-canada-dong-dang-cai-world-cup-2026-421-188418.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: M\u1ef9 - Mexico \u2013 Canada \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2026</span><br />\r\n\u0110\u00fang m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018, FIFA ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh t\u00ednh n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c k\u1ef3 World Cup 2026.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1235","checkdouble":"191145"},{"date":"08:10 14/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 (17h00 ng\u00e0y 14/7): C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong t\u1ea7m tay","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/nhan-dinh-hagl-vs-can-tho-17h00-ngay-147-co-hoi-trong-tam-tay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn HAGL vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u1edd m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f9ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 HAGL s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u1eafm l\u1ea5y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ra \u0111\u00f2n knock-out tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch.</h2><h2>Th\u1eddi c\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB HAGL \u0111ang c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong 4 n\u0103m qua. S\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111ang gi\u00fap HAGL tr\u1edf n\u00ean &lsquo;c\u1ee9ng c\u00e1p&rsquo; h\u01a1n \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i V-League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 18 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6 tr\u00ean BXH r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ch\u1eaft chiu t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch cao nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1eb7p XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e0 kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 &lsquo;G\u1ed7&rsquo; s\u1edf h\u1eefu 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. 14 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn 6 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 (17h00 ng\u00e0y 147) C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong t\u1ea7m tay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 (17h00 ng\u00e0y 147) C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong t\u1ea7m tay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/3/Nhan-dinh-HAGL-vs-Can-Tho-(17h00-ngay-147)-Co-hoi-trong-tam-tay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>&nbsp;C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn&nbsp;\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 T\u00e2y \u0110\u00f4 \u0111ang &lsquo;r\u01a1i t\u1ef1 do&rsquo; tr\u00ean BXH V-League. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 11 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng TP.HCM \u0111\u00fang 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n ti\u1ebfp theo t\u1ea1i Pleiku c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecd v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nguy hi\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do d\u1eabn t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 sa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 vi\u1ec7c l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n s\u00e2u sa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u00ec ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1n l\u00f3t tay n\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang phong \u0111\u1ed9. Ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a th\u00f4ng tin n\u00f3i tr\u00ean nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y \u0110\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-5 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n C\u1ea7m Ph\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y th\u00ec m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai l\u00e0 k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc cho c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 ch\u01b0a cho th\u1ea5y d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u s\u1ebd tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi &ldquo;v\u0169ng l\u1ea7y&rdquo;, 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau trong t\u1ea7m tay c\u1ee7a HAGL. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i g\u00e1nh ch\u1ecbu sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9 v\u1eeba qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng quan hai \u0111\u1ed9i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y, HAGL \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1. Hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 to\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y t\u1ea1i Pleiku. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp theo v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o y\u00ean t\u00e2m v\u1ec1 hai ngo\u1ea1i binh Josip Zeba v\u00e0 Osmar Francisco khi c\u1ea3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean lo ng\u1ea1i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u1ed1n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n \u1edf 2 v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n thua nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi 32 b\u00e0n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 mong manh c\u1ee7a &lsquo;G\u1ed7&rsquo;. S\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 28 b\u00e0n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Van Toan ghi cu dup ban thang cho HAGL\" title=\"V\u0103n To\u00e0n ghi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/van-toan-ghi-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, HAGL c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean HAGL c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1edfi h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League</span>. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Pleiku \u0111ang duy tr\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 5 v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 4 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u00e0n. L\u00fac n\u00e0y C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 7 b\u00e0n trong khi V\u0103n To\u00e0n, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i V-League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1eb7p C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111ang &lsquo;r\u1ed1i nh\u01b0 t\u01a1 v\u00f2&rsquo;, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00ed do \u0111\u1ec3 tin v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a &lsquo;G\u1ed7&rsquo; \u1edf v\u00f2ng 19 V-League sau hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u00f9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, HAGL s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1eaft chiu c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf b\u1ed9 l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, v\u1ed1n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n tr\u1eadn HAGL vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL: V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn, Josip Zeba, H\u1ed3ng Duy, V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n Thanh, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0110\u00f4ng Tri\u1ec1u, Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1: V\u0129nh L\u1ee3i, H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng, Ho\u00e0ng Vissai, Cao C\u01b0\u1eddng, C\u00f4ng Th\u00e0nh, Ng\u1ecdc Anh, Th\u00e0nh L\u1ed9c, Quang T\u00ecnh, T\u0103ng Tu\u1ea5n, Luiz, Patiyo.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-vong-19-vleague-co-hoi-cho-hagl-168-191117.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/truoc-vong-19-vleague-co-hoi-cho-hagl.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-vong-19-vleague-co-hoi-cho-hagl-168-191117.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 19 V-League: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho HAGL</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i l\u00e0 XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, CLB HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf v\u00f2ng 19 V-League cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1234","checkdouble":"191146"},{"date":"08:55 14/07","title":"Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: HLV Simeone \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean cho Griezmann","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/13/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-hlv-simeone-dua-ra-loi-khuyen-cho-griezmann.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai 15/7, HLV Diego Simeone \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Griezmann \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</h2><h2>HLV Simeone \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean cho Griezmann</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 HLV Simeone \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean cho Griez h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 HLV Simeone \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean cho Griez h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/15/Chung-ket-World-Cup-2018-HLV-Simeone-dua-ra-loi-khuyen-cho-Griez-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV\u00a0Simeone \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 Griezmann\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Antoine Griezmann \u0111ang r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch khi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. L\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Atletico Madrid \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Griezmann l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lo ng\u1ea1i c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u00e2m l\u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Atletico Madrid, Diego Simeone \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Griezmann k\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i: \"\u00d4ng \u1ea5y (Simeone) n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i h\u00e3y t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft trong \u0111\u00eam \u0111\u00f3, r\u1ed3i nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u1eadp trung cho tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. HLV Simeone mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a xong, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. T\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0 ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf hai tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Champions League 2015/16 v\u00e0 Euro 2016. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \"\u0111\u1ed5i v\u1eadn\" \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua khi c\u00f9ng Atletico l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u1edf Europa League. N\u1ebfu thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi, anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-phap-se-vo-dich-421-191099.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-phap-se-vo-dich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-phap-se-vo-dich-421-191099.html\">Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: 4 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin \u0110T Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Croatia. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Deschamps s\u1ebd l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/modric-toi-san-sang-doi-3-cup-c1-de-vo-dich-world-cup-469-191113.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/modric-toi-san-sang-doi-3-cup-c1-de-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/modric-toi-san-sang-doi-3-cup-c1-de-vo-dich-world-cup-469-191113.html\">Modric: T\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i 4 c\u00fap C1 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Modric kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi anh. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u00f2n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u Champions...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ivan-perisic-tiet-lo-ly-do-giup-croatia-co-the-danh-bai-phap-421-191086.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/ivan-perisic-tiet-lo-ly-do-giup-croatia-co-the-danh-bai-phap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ivan-perisic-tiet-lo-ly-do-giup-croatia-co-the-danh-bai-phap-421-191086.html\">Ivan Perisic ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Croatia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p</span><br>\r\nIvan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Les Bleus trong tr\u1eadn chung...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1233","checkdouble":"191147"},{"date":"19:21 13/07","title":"HLV Emery h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n Arsenal s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/24/hlv-emery-hua-hen-arsenal-se-co-them-bom-tan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra nh\u01b0ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1edbn n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 tham v\u1ecdng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c mua s\u1eafm</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 5 t\u00e2n binh trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 bao g\u1ed3m Lucas Torreira, Bernd Leno, Sokratis Papastathopoulos, Matteo Guendouzi v\u00e0 Stephan Lichtsteiner. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng vi\u00ean g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng n\u00ean tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Unai Emery t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho nh\u1eefng Per Mertesacker, Jack Wilshere v\u00e0 Santi Cazorla \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Arsenal. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/HLV-Emery-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lucas Torreira l\u00e0 1 trong 5 t\u00e2n binh Arsenal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn kh\u00f4ng khi n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cH\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1ed5n. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c mua s\u1eafm khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1edf c\u1eeda v\u1edbi \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i mua b\u00e1n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m. V\u00e0 Emery d\u00f9 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Emery tro thanh HLV Arsenal\" title=\"Emery tro thanh HLV Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/Arsenal-chieu-mo-Torreira-Tuong-lai-bat-dau-tu-hom-nay-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal v\u00e0 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n \"bom t\u1ea5n\"</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 khi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1ecd\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 46 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i. \u201cTh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u1eb7c ch\u01a1i d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 xem li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho Arsenal hay kh\u00f4ng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Emery tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Arsenal s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Boreham Wood cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1edbi Singapore d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-hang-hot-ligue-1-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191053.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: H\u00e0ng hot Ligue 1 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-so-huu-tan-binh-thu-5-172-190980.html\">N\u00d3NG: Arsenal ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 5</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-xac-nhan-co-tan-binh-thu-4-tri-gia-30-trieu-euro-172-190886.html\">Arsenal CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 4 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-arsenal-chi-35-trieu-euro-mua-andre-gomes-172-190877.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Andre Gomes?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/wenger-bat-bai-khoi-arsenal-vikante-172-190866.html\">Wenger b\u1eadt b\u00e3i kh\u1ecfi Arsenal v\u00ec...Kante?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-bernd-leno-chinh-thuc-chon-so-ao-o-arsenal-172-190840.html\">T\u00e2n binh Bernd Leno ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 \u00e1o \u1edf Arsenal</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1232","checkdouble":"191120"},{"date":"20:00 13/07","title":"M\u01b0\u1ee3n oai Ronaldo, Juventus t\u00ednh t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/15/muon-oai-ronaldo-juventus-tinh-tai-hop-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba c\u1ee7a Man United. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t Miralem Pjanic v\u00e0o tay c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d hy v\u1ecdng uy danh c\u1ee7a si\u00eau t\u00e2n binh Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0a Pogba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ch\u1ed1n x\u01b0a.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pjanic b\u1ecb chi\u00eau d\u1ee5</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus t\u1eeb AS Roma \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2016/17, Miralem Pjanic \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia & Herzegovina \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed7i khi v\u1eafng \u0111i Pjanic, Juventus l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c lao \u0111ao \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Bianconeri hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M\u01b0\u1ee3n oai Ronaldo, Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba c\u1ee7a Man United h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"M\u01b0\u1ee3n oai Ronaldo, Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba c\u1ee7a Man United h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/24/Muon-oai-Ronaldo,-Juventus-muon-mua-Pogba-cua-Man-United-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pjanic \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Barca v\u00e0 Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t n\u1eb1m \u1edf vi\u1ec7c Pjanic c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Barcelona hay Man City. Juventus kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 5 s\u1ebd m\u1ed9t l\u00f2ng, m\u1ed9t d\u1ea1 v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juve t\u00ednh t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t, Juventus thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Pjanic \u1edf l\u1ea1i. M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, h\u1ecd t\u00ednh s\u1eb5n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n B n\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n x\u1ea3y ra. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba c\u1ee7a Man United \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Pjanic \u1edf khu trung tuy\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Paul Pogba\" title=\"tien ve Paul Pogba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/messi-muon-barca-mua-ban-hop-dong-dat-gia-nhat-lich-su-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba c\u1ee7a Man United</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2016, Juve \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Pjanic v\u1ec1 thay Pogba gia nh\u1eadp M.U v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u chuy\u1ebfn quay l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u1ee7a Pogba t\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay kh\u00f4ng su\u00f4n s\u1ebb nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh. Anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9 v\u00e0 b\u1ecb t\u1eeb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn Anh t\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Pjanic \u0111i theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a Barca hay Man City, Juventus d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a Pogba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin m\u1edbi chi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus hy v\u1ecdng tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng Ronaldo s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Pogba m\u1ee7i l\u00f2ng. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Pjanic (n\u1ebfu anh ra \u0111i) c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Allianz sau 2 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/luka-modric-noi-gi-khi-ronaldo-toi-juventus-180-191085.html\">Luka Modric n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mu-day-manh-qua-trinh-mua-gareth-bale-180-191077.html\">M.U \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u201csao b\u1ef1\u201d Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-phai-toi-juventus-vi-messi-184-191064.html\">Ronaldo ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi Juventus v\u00ec\u2026 Messi?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-sang-juve-quan-domino-tren-ttcn-da-do-421-191051.html\">Ronaldo sang Juve: Qu\u00e2n domino tr\u00ean TTCN \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1231","checkdouble":"191121"}]}